&lt;h1&gt;Staff Nurse, Biologics Day Unit – Band 5&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The biologics day unit is looking for an enthusiastic Staff Nurse with experience to join our team. The successful candidate must be proactive and willing to learn as the job encompasses a plethora of different skills from the administration of cytotoxic drugs to running venesection lists.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Biologics Day Unit is a fast paced infusion suite where we treat patients from a range of specialities: rheumatology, gastroenterology, ophthalmology, immunology and more.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our patients are often regular attenders and our team pride themselves on the excellent rapport they build with our patients over the years, many who suffer with debilitating long term conditions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate must be approachable and friendly and able to communicate clearly with patients as some of the procedures require one to one care.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are ideally looking for a very experience nurses who have a proven record of cannulation and venepuncture as we expect the successful candidate to develop skills to venesect patients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details please contact Andi Ferreira on 01225 821022 or bleep 7488.&lt;/p&gt;
